---
title: One-Pan Spanish Chorizo & Couscous Stew with Aioli & Lemon
description: The beauty of this smokey paella-style stew is that all of the flavours cook together into a sauce that’s equal parts sweet, savoury
and powerful. We love the boost you get from the mild chorizo and blistered capsicum – we promise it’s never tasted as good!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
